                strong Every 3 months:
                |  Adult boosters
            .prevention-tips
              .symptoms-title ğŸ›¡ï¸ Prevention Tips:
              p Maintain biosecurity, vaccinate on schedule, quarantine new birds, and ensure proper ventilation.

